{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1726422, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "推荐《游戏改变世界》", "timestamp": 1621960909, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726435, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "😅", "timestamp": 1621960948, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726438, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你自己多玩玩一些游戏就知道了，大多是图一时爽快和成就感", "timestamp": 1621960963, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726439, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以我玩switch", "timestamp": 1621960967, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726441, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "为了多巴胺啊，游戏提供的实时反馈是学习给不了的", "timestamp": 1621960978, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726450, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz玩游戏，是因为不想写作业，不想考虑将来要写的作业，不想思考自己的未来，不想去想国家、民族的命运。\n每当我离开电脑屏幕，我就会被深深的焦虑所包围，如何摆脱焦虑？打游戏", "timestamp": 1621961060, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726464, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "知道宁勤奋了，下一个", "timestamp": 1621961125, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726467, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不管怎么样这个点还搞出噪声影响别人就是nt", "timestamp": 1621961139, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726474, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "游戏玩多了真的会烦，大部分游戏都是一个优化问题，你打的多了，模型训练的差不多了，玩起游戏也千篇一律，可是不玩真的会焦虑，nmd，就和抽烟一样，明知道对身体不好，可是不抽几口谁顶得住啊", "timestamp": 1621961180, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726496, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": 1726422, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 如果说游戏形成了人与游戏的闭环，那么生活中的游戏化又何从谈起呢qaq。btw dz没看过这本书好像没资格这样说哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1621961383, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1726518, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 339373, "reply_to": 1726422, "tag": null, "text": "我很爱生活，也尝尝尝试不同的东西，但新鲜感总是稍纵即逝。在这个意义上， 游戏确实能够使生活在一瞬间变得有趣，不过这又很难解释老玩家会变成老玩家的原因了", "timestamp": 1621961563, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 339373, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "真诚提问，非引战\n玩电脑游戏究竟是为了什么呢？室友现在还在打游戏（主要是吵的一批），在dz的视角看来就很难理解。如果从最消极的角度来看，就是以时间换数据，以一时之爽快换未来之空虚。dz也有很多这样的体验，不知道dym怎么看", "timestamp": 1621960861, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1621961562, "url": "", "vote": {}}}